  MODULE .......: BEITEMPL.P
  TASK .........: SHOW Billing Event Items of one Price event/one Price list
  APPLICATION ..: nn
  AUTHOR .......: pt
  CREATED ......: 28-09-99
  CHANGED ......: 04-10-99 jp urights added
                  15.09.03/aam brand
  Version ......: M15
